Package: factcheckr
Type: Package
Title: Sentiment Analysis Package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Armel Oum Maemble
Maintainer: Armel Oum Maemble <smaemble@tamu.edu>
Description: factcheckr provides functions for analyzing text data including but 
    not limited to functions for text cleanup, text tokenization, top terms, word frequencies, 
    and Sentiment Analysis(SA) just to name a few. SA serves as a comprehensive term encompassing 
    methodologies that extract emotional or opinion-related insights from natural language. 
    SA has proven effective in scrutinizing language data across various fields, including psychology,
    economics, education, as well as political and social sciences. Typically, SA is utilized to 
    ascertain the collective perspective of a broader group of speakers regarding a specific 
    phenomenon, be it political figures, parties, product lines, or situations.
